---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Risk Disclaimer — Meridian',
  description: 'Important risk disclosure and legal disclaimer for Meridian trading psychology software.',
  robots: { index: true, follow: true },
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- ───────────────────────── HERO ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="halo">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 md:pt-24 pb-12 text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-6">LEGAL &middot; RISK DISCLOSURE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 leading-[1.05]">
        Risk Disclaimer
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        Please read this disclaimer carefully before using Meridian.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── DISCLOSURE BODY ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="border-y border-zinc-200 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-24">

      <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-400 bg-amber-50 p-6 md:p-7 mb-12">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold text-amber-700 mb-2 eyebrow">IMPORTANT NOTICE</p>
        <p class="text-amber-900 font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Trading futures, forex, and other financial instruments involves substantial risk of loss and is not suitable for all investors. Before using this software, please read and understand this entire disclaimer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Risk of Loss</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Trading commodity futures contracts, options, and forex involves substantial risk of loss. The risk of loss in trading commodity futures can be substantial. You should therefore carefully consider whether such trading is suitable for you in light of your financial condition. The high degree of leverage that is often obtainable in commodity interest trading can work against you as well as for you. The possibility exists that you could sustain a total loss of funds deposited and may be required to deposit additional funds to maintain your position.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Software Purpose — Not Financial Advice</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Meridian is a <strong class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">psychological monitoring and behavioral risk enforcement tool</strong>. It does not:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold shrink-0">&check;</span><span>Provide trading signals, buy/sell recommendations, or market analysis</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold shrink-0">&check;</span><span>Constitute financial advice, investment advice, or any other form of professional advice</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold shrink-0">&check;</span><span>Predict or guarantee future trading results or outcomes</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold shrink-0">&check;</span><span>Replace the judgment of a qualified financial advisor</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            The Psychological Stability Index (PSI) displayed by Meridian reflects patterns derived from user-configured behavioral inputs during a trading session. It is intended solely as a personal awareness tool. All trading decisions remain entirely the responsibility of the user.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Past Performance</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Past performance results are not necessarily indicative of future results. Any trading results discussed, referenced, or implied in connection with this software do not guarantee or imply similar results in the future. All trading involves risk. Substantial risk of loss exists.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">No Guarantee of Results</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Meridian makes no guarantees regarding improvement in trading performance, consistency, profitability, or reduction of trading losses as a result of using this software. Individual results will vary significantly based on personal trading methods, market conditions, risk management practices, and other factors outside this software's scope.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Regulatory Compliance</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            It is your responsibility to comply with all applicable laws and regulations in your jurisdiction regarding the use of trading software and the execution of trades. Meridian does not accept liability for any regulatory violations resulting from your trading activities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Software Accuracy</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            While Meridian is developed with care, the software is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We do not warrant that the software will be error-free, uninterrupted, or that it will operate without defects. We are not liable for any losses, damages, or missed opportunities arising from technical errors, software failures, or incorrect calculations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Third-Party Platform</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Meridian is an <strong class="font-semibold text-zinc-800">Official NinjaTrader Ecosystem Vendor</strong> &mdash; audited and approved by NinjaTrader's Compliance, QA, and Executive teams. NinjaTrader® is a registered trademark of NinjaTrader LLC, and Meridian is operated by an independent company &mdash; it is not owned by NinjaTrader LLC. Use of Meridian in conjunction with NinjaTrader is subject to NinjaTrader's own terms of service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-zinc-200" />

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Risk Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Futures and forex trading contains substantial risk and is not for every investor. An investor could potentially lose all or more than the initial investment. Risk capital is money that can be lost without jeopardizing one's financial security or lifestyle. Only risk capital should be used for trading and only those with sufficient risk capital should consider trading. Past performance is not necessarily indicative of future results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Hypothetical Performance Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Hypothetical performance results have many inherent limitations, some of which are described below. No representation is being made that any account will or is likely to achieve profits or losses similar to those shown; in fact, there are frequently sharp differences between hypothetical performance results and the actual results subsequently achieved by any particular trading program. One of the limitations of hypothetical performance results is that they are generally prepared with the benefit of hindsight. In addition, hypothetical trading does not involve financial risk, and no hypothetical trading record can completely account for the impact of financial risk of actual trading. For example, the ability to withstand losses or to adhere to a particular trading program in spite of trading losses are material points which can also adversely affect actual trading results. There are numerous other factors related to the markets in general or to the implementation of any specific trading program which cannot be fully accounted for in the preparation of hypothetical performance results and all which can adversely affect trading results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Testimonial Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Testimonials appearing on this website may not be representative of other clients or customers and are not a guarantee of future performance or success.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">Consult a Professional</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            You should seek advice from an independent, qualified financial advisor before engaging in any trading activity. Nothing on this website or in the Meridian software should be interpreted as a recommendation to trade any specific instrument or to adopt any particular trading strategy.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-12 border-t border-zinc-200 pt-6">
        Last updated: June 2026. This disclaimer is subject to change. Please check this page regularly for updates.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
